<br />
<br />Hell no. Supporting incorrect clones is up to the individual author. Really no one should bother supporting it unless their target market is one that the NES or Famicom was not officially released in. Even still, the hope would be that someone would fully clone the NES <strong>correctly</strong> instead.

		

